1
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,340
It's been three years.

2
00:00:12,970 --> 00:00:15,100
To take over this prominent position,

3
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:18,410
every step feels like
walking on knife edges.

4
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:20,600
Though the truth is still hidden

5
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:23,130
in the flickering candlelight
of the palace,

6
00:00:23,350 --> 00:00:24,670
we have used our blood

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,710
to melt the icy steps

8
00:00:26,710 --> 00:00:28,510
leading to Dacang's golden age.

9
00:01:37,490 --> 00:01:40,660
[Luminosity Behind The Palace]

10
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:06,620
Why are the imperial guards
missing in the inner court?

11
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:26,060
Your Majesty.

12
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:29,800
Who are you?

13
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,960
Red silk ribbons?

14
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,480
So you guys...

15
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,530
are from Prince Ji's Mansion?

16
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:42,960
Prince Ji is trying to rebel!

17
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,350
Imperial guards of the inner court,
attention!

18
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:46,210
Kill all the traitors you can see!

19
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,150
Hurry! Send the signal!

20
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:09,100
[Xuanji Pavilion]

21
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:23,170
[Map of the Nine Kingdoms]

22
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,130
[Dacang]

23
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:29,070
[Xuanji Pavilion]

24
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,460
The rebel, Yin Changyan!

25
00:03:57,740 --> 00:03:58,470
Arrest him!

26
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:17,980
Your Highness.

27
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:22,060
The Xuanji Pavilion and the inner court
are both under our control now.

28
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:24,640
Her Majesty's Xuanji Pavilion
is an imperial restricted area.

29
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,840
Just let me meet with Her Majesty alone.

30
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:27,600
Yes!

31
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:31,810
[Xuanji Pavilion]

32
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,000
Clean this place up.

33
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,560
Yes!

34
00:04:39,659 --> 00:04:43,360
[Xuanji Pavilion]

35
00:04:57,370 --> 00:04:59,220
[Xuanji Pavilion]

36
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,260
You're really trying to ally with Qin Qiu

37
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:05,920
and persecute
the loyal and upright officials!

38
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,520
Mother, after you abdicate,

39
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:09,270
I will find ways

40
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:11,270
to resolve the grudges
among the four major families

41
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:13,630
so that they can serve the country
ruled by our Yin family

42
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,290
to ensure the peace of Dacang.

43
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,690
You want me to abdicate?

44
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,830
Yin Changyan.

45
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:21,150
This is just like
asking a tiger for its skin!

46
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:25,080
Mother, you're getting old after all.

47
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,880
Though the strong tiger is fierce,

48
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,990
I believe that

49
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,480
as long as it's used properly,

50
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,920
it's still okay to use it.

51
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,810
Changyan.

52
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,560
I am not dead yet.

53
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,020
Yin Changyan.

54
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:42,340
If you insist on
siding with the noble families,

55
00:05:42,630 --> 00:05:42,920
I will...

56
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,950
[Xuanji Pavilion]

57
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:46,200
strip you of your title as Prince Ji

58
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,940
and then get another heir,

59
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,680
which is a good option for me!

60
00:05:50,850 --> 00:05:51,909
If that's the case,

61
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:53,430
then I have no choice but to

62
00:05:53,430 --> 00:05:55,490
perform my final act of filial piety.

63
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:02,270
I'm respectfully urging Your Majesty
to abdicate quickly

64
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:04,070
and enjoy your remaining years.

65
00:06:05,450 --> 00:06:07,710
You ungrateful son!

66
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,820
Changyan, stop!

67
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:14,080
Who's there?

68
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,160
[Xuanji Pavilion]

69
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,070
Changyan!

70
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:16,450
Arrest her!

71
00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:17,190
[Xuanji Pavilion]

72
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:17,950
Stop!

73
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,220
Your Majesty!

74
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:31,820
Step back!

75
00:06:41,690 --> 00:06:42,490
Your Majesty.

76
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:55,040
[Xuanji Pavilion]

77
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:57,700
Yin Changyan.

78
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:01,000
Why are you doing this?

79
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:05,450
Since I'm a member of the imperial family,

80
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,310
stop asking me why.

81
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,530
Is it just...

82
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:15,470
Is it just for that imperial robe?

83
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:21,090
Su Leyu, you shouldn't have come here.

84
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:24,640
Your Highness, you're the one
who shouldn't be here.

85
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,530
Yin Changyan...

86
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,700
forced Her Majesty to abdicate
and killed Her Majesty.

87
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,690
After making this move,

88
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,360
in this chess game,

89
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:50,010
there will be no turning back
for you anymore.

90
00:07:50,130 --> 00:07:54,420
[Xuanji Pavilion]

91
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,500
Don't force me to do it.

92
00:08:14,330 --> 00:08:14,940
Yin Cong!

93
00:08:14,970 --> 00:08:16,730
Your Highness, are you going to

94
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,950
kill both Leyu and me?

95
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:30,120
Let's go!

96
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,320
Come on!

97
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:39,860
Let's go!

98
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:40,940
Your Highness!

99
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:42,230
Let's go!

100
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:45,200
Your Highness!

101
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:47,050
We can't let them leave alive.

102
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,410
Just let them go.

103
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:52,580
Yin Cong.

104
00:08:52,730 --> 00:08:54,020
Why were you at the Xuanji Pavilion?

105
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:55,640
Prince Qi told me someone was trying to
force Her Majesty to abdicate.

106
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,150
He asked me to come and save Her Majesty.

107
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:57,840
Yin Cong!

108
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,480
Leyu.

109
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,000
Let's go to the barracks in Zhongdu first.

110
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,600
There's someone who I know there.

111
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,720
Once the city gates open,

112
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,080
let's escape through the waterway

113
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,210
and hide for a while.

114
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:07,920
Yin Cong, I'm not leaving.

115
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:10,880
Leyu.

116
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,840
He has changed.

117
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,200
He has even forced the empress to abdicate
and killed her.

118
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,060
Why do you still want to stay here?

119
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,220
Let's leave together.

120
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,000
Yin Cong, I can't escape.

121
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,490
I shouldn't leave, either.

122
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:26,360
If I leave,

123
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:27,840
the truth about tonight's incident

124
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,900
will never be revealed to the public.

125
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:33,570
What else do you want to investigate?

126
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:36,000
You saw what he did, didn't you?

127
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,130
Today, with Prince Ji
putting on that imperial robe,

128
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:44,390
you and I have become
pieces in this chess game.

129
00:09:46,110 --> 00:09:47,770
I'd like to see with my own eyes

130
00:09:49,110 --> 00:09:50,480
how Prince Ji

131
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:54,630
will rule this country.

132
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:57,910
Yin Cong.

133
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,470
Leave at once.

134
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:02,710
Go!

135
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:20,280
This entire Zhongdu City
is beneath our feet now.

136
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,840
Now that we can see such scenery,

137
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,440
it's truly worth it

138
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,640
to have lied to our teacher and come out.

139
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:28,360
This Zhongdu City
is just like a chessboard.

140
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,840
And we're the black and white pieces
in this chess game.

141
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,630
One day,

142
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:34,130
we will hold the pieces ourselves

143
00:10:34,450 --> 00:10:35,220
and build

144
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:37,140
the State of Dacang together.

145
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,200
That's a deal.

146
00:11:28,610 --> 00:11:29,860
[Memorial Tablet
of Sacred and Supreme Empress Wu]

147
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:31,520
[In the 29th year of Jianing,]

148
00:11:31,890 --> 00:11:32,730
[Empress Wu, Yin Fu, passed away.]

149
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:34,940
[Memorial Tablet
of Sacred and Supreme Empress Wu]

150
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:36,790
[Taiji Palace]

151
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,270
[Prince Ji, Yin Changyan,]

152
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,670
[inherited the throne.]

153
00:11:39,890 --> 00:11:42,490
[The reign title was changed
to be Shengyuan.]

154
00:11:44,110 --> 00:11:46,770
[The three noble families
were soon promoted.]

155
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:50,020
[Premier Qin Qiu
was promoted to Grand Preceptor.]

156
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:52,630
[Wang Zhan was promoted to
Minister of the Ministry of Justice.]

157
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:56,090
[Xi Zimo was promoted to
Minister of the Ministry of Revenue.]

158
00:11:56,180 --> 00:11:59,000
[With the imperial decree, Qin Jiaoqiong,
Qin Qiu's daughter, entered the palace]

159
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:01,370
[and was conferred
the title of Consort Shu.]

160
00:12:01,370 --> 00:12:03,080
[Marquis Jingyuan, Su Wencheng,]

161
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,540
[was demoted
to guard the northern border.]

162
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,690
[Prince Qi, Yin Zhiyi,]

163
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:12,180
[went to the fief immediately
to be the vassal king there.]

164
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:13,670
[Central Palace Gate]

165
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:16,470
[Princess Zhaoyang, Yin Cong,
was disrespectful to the emperor.]

166
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:17,730
[From today onwards,]

167
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:20,410
[she'll have to
guard the imperial mausoleum.]

168
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:24,000
May Your Majesty
receive Heaven's blessings,

169
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,720
enjoy the grace of Earth,

170
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,610
have people's allegiance,

171
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:29,510
rule the country eternally

172
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:31,640
and live as long as Heaven does.

173
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,740
By the late empress's decree,

174
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,150
Su Leyu,

175
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,720
who entered the palace at a young age,

176
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,080
has won my favor.

177
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,000
The title of Consort Xian
will be bestowed on her

178
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,550
on an auspicious day.

179
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:48,640
Leyu.

180
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:50,520
He has changed.

181
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,750
He has even forced the empress to abdicate
and killed her.

182
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,610
Why do you still want to stay here?

183
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,510
My Lady.

184
00:13:02,810 --> 00:13:05,150
The conferment ceremony
will be held in a few days.

185
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:07,000
What if His Majesty sees this?

186
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,190
Yin Changyan.

187
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,750
I would rather die

188
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:18,030
than marry a usurper.

189
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:22,080
His Majesty is here!

190
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:01,090
Greetings, Your Majesty.

191
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,920
Please forgive my rudeness.

192
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:05,200
I don't dare to accept the gifts

193
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,320
from Your Majesty.

194
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,120
But as for my own stuff,

195
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:13,540
please return it to me, Your Majesty.

196
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:16,720
Leyu.

197
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,630
Changyan, this is a gift for you.

198
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,440
This knot is called Brocade Knotâ€Œ,

199
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,390
which is also known as Six-Petal Knot.

200
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:26,750
It symbolizes success in everything

201
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:28,210
and a bright future ahead.

202
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:30,890
Do you like it?

203
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:32,840
Yes, I do.

204
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,510
Your stuff?

205
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:52,410
All things in the country
belong to the emperor.

206
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:55,950
How could you call it your stuff?

207
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:06,200
The late empress taught me this principle.

208
00:15:06,690 --> 00:15:08,350
It's better to shatter as jade

209
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,170
than survive as a tile.

210
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,670
It's the late empress's decree

211
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:16,070
to let you enter the palace
and be a consort.

212
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:18,220
I really can't submit myself

213
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,240
to a usurper.

214
00:15:21,330 --> 00:15:22,730
With such disobedience,

215
00:15:23,970 --> 00:15:25,770
aren't you afraid I'll kill you?

216
00:15:27,050 --> 00:15:30,250
As a member of the Su family,
how would I be afraid of death?

217
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:37,610
Your Majesty,

218
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,980
please grant me death.

219
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:56,410
So what you mean is that

220
00:15:57,910 --> 00:15:59,200
you would rather die

221
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:01,330
than enter the palace to be my consort?

222
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,840
Do you really hate me so much?

223
00:16:10,430 --> 00:16:11,630
Should I not hate you?

224
00:16:25,450 --> 00:16:26,910
It's not difficult to die.

225
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:30,120
I have already reported our marriage

226
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:32,380
to the ancestors at the Imperial Temple.

227
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,270
Now in front of you,

228
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:35,800
there are only two options.

229
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:37,350
You can either

230
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:40,330
put on the wedding gown
and be my Consort Xian

231
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:44,590
or kneel and kowtow
at the Imperial Temple by yourself

232
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:47,770
to beg forgiveness from the late empress.

233
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:52,210
I'll obey the imperial decree.

234
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,980
Do you really hate me so much?

235
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,580
It's better to shatter as jade

236
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:44,590
than survive as a tile.

237
00:17:55,090 --> 00:17:56,930
Leyu, one day if you marry me,

238
00:17:58,430 --> 00:18:01,230
I'll personally make a crown
for your coronation.

239
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:04,610
How about making it with these camellias?

240
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:17,120
Changyan.

241
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:19,350
Being an emperor

242
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:22,970
means enduring a life of loneliness.

243
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:28,010
You'll have to hide the truth
from everyone,

244
00:18:29,770 --> 00:18:31,130
including Leyu.

245
00:18:38,570 --> 00:18:39,370
Your Majesty!

246
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:42,040
Your Majesty!

247
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:43,360
Bad news!

248
00:18:43,930 --> 00:18:45,790
Marquis Jingyuan, Su Wencheng...

249
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:47,720
Su Wencheng had an accident!

250
00:18:50,690 --> 00:18:51,310
Brother.
